I can't wait to try this! To Drippin, no -- you definitely do not want to use jack o'lantern pumpkins -- they are not bred for flavor but for size so they taste pretty icky. Most grocery stores now carry pie pumpkins, and that's what you will want to use. Better yet, try your local farmers market!

